data.title: Darlington BC
data.meta_description: Making payments online and over the phone for Council Tax, Rent, Parking fines, invoices, business rates, mortgages and benefit overpayments.
data.text:
Make a payment

or call 0300 4562671

We offer a 24 hours a day, 7 days a week service for paying:

Council tax

Rent

Parking fines

Invoices

Business rates (NDR)

Benefit overpayments

Mortgages and loan repayment

Enforcement fines

Educational fines

Marriage/Registrar Bookings

These can be paid by Visa, Mastercard, Delta, Maestro and Solo debit and credit Cards.

How else can I pay?

Council tax,

business rates,

housing rents,

invoices,

benefit overpayments

and mortgages
